This is a great little sandwich shop which serves fresh bread, quality meats, fat sliced french fries, and the best frozen drink out there.   The Eegee drink is really the best thing out there. It is pretty hard to describe exactly what sets this frozen fruit slush apart from the rest but it is literally unmatched. It is a perfect consistency of air, flavored ice, and real pieces of fruit. The regular flavors are Lemon, Strawberry, and Pina Colada and a four flavor varies by the month as a flavor of the month. My son has decided he wants this instead of a birthday cake for his upcoming birthday.

